author: philip
msg: When updating the rep-cache database only look for existing rows if
the insert fails.  This means adding new representations requires only
(svn_fs_fs__set_rep_reference): Insert first, check existing only on fail.

author: ppoddar
msg: OPENJPA-2017: Modify test to adjust for changes in AutoDetach constant

author: aconway
msg: Problem: the first broker in the cluster could be killed before the
receiver was connected, so the receiver could not fail-over, it didn't
have a failover update. Fix: wait for the first message to be received
by the receiver before starting the broker-kill loop.
